{"tid":2069367,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"范鴻齡：想以罷工威脅醫管局的人絕對不會得逞","createTime":"2020-06-18T10:22:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T12:43:45.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7a506e4fb63d182033376c720634a332ca44c521","tid":2069367,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:22:26.000Z","msg":"反對港區國安法的多個工會正籌備公投及罷工，醫管局員工陣線亦曾表示會響應。醫管局主席范鴻齡說，絕不接受醫管局員工將政治行為帶進醫管局，影響服務提供，令病人權益受損。<br />\n<br />\n他強調醫管局一向沒有政治立場，醫管局的職責是為所有病人提供最好的服務、救急扶危，同事可以有政治立場，但前提是不可以將政治理念帶進醫管局。<br />\n<br />\n范鴻齡說，有聲音想透過罷工，威脅醫管局認同某些人的政治理念，他指出，這些人絕對不會得逞，如果有人罷工，醫管局會根據既定機制處理。<br />\n<br />\n被問到如何處理二月參與罷工的醫護人員，范鴻齡表示，醫管局已經外聘律師處理，團隊包括大律師及資深大律師等，已交由人事部跟進，有進一步消息再作公布。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532835-20200618.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532835-20200618.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHmlQkZRBUTTGMtnLt8L03NM%3D&h=f49ed66e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532835-20200618.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ebcf4995\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532835-20200618.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"45c95c91fe1cf70922147277826ce5363566cdd0","tid":2069367,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:47:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8OMXVDD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8OMXVDD.jpg&h=a1de48a8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YT0edqj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYT0edqj.jpg&h=5e851e73&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29994aba8f1904e73a4525806d24b2ed9a7f4254","tid":2069367,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T12:43:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}